## Transformation Phases

<!--
  Customize this plan:
  - Add phases: copy a phase block and define objective + scope
  - Remove phases: delete the block or comment it out
  - Reorder: move blocks up/down to change execution order
  - Mark parallel: add (parallel) tag to phases that can run simultaneously

  Dependencies:
  - Phase 1 (Config & Docs) must run first (other phases depend on .chama.yml)
  - Phases marked (parallel) run concurrently and merge before dependent phases
  - Phase 4 (Quality Gates) should run after tests are created
-->

### Phase 1: Config & Docs
- Objective: Generate Chama configuration and documentation
- Scope:
  - .chama.yml with quality gates
  - CLAUDE.md, README.md, PROJECT_BRIEF.md
  - LICENSE (if chosen)
  - Install recommended plugins

### Phase 2: Test Infrastructure (parallel)
- Objective: Install and configure test framework
- Scope:
  - Install test framework for {{STACK}}
  - Configure test scripts
  - Install E2E framework if frontend exists

### Phase 3: Minimum Tests
- Objective: Reach coverage target ({{COVERAGE_TARGET}}%)
- Scope:
  - Unit tests for business logic
  - Integration tests for API endpoints
  - E2E tests for critical user flows

### Phase 4: Quality Gates & Hardening
- Objective: Configure and validate quality gates
- Scope:
  - Run gate-check, address CRITICAL findings
  - Configure quality gates in .chama.yml
  - Verify all gates pass

### Phase 5: CI Integration (parallel)
- Objective: Add test step to CI pipeline
- Scope:
  - Detect CI provider
  - Add test command to pipeline

### Phase 6: Hooks Setup (parallel)
- Objective: Configure pre-commit and PR hooks
- Scope:
  - Pre-commit: lint + typecheck
  - PR gate: full tests + gate-check

